<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5329421>
    dc:description "Figs 25–33. 25–27 – Macrosiagon callewaerti Pic, 1950; holotype. (25 – habitus dorsally; 26 – head frontally; 27 – metatarsomeres dorsally). 28–30 – Macrosiagon grombczewskii (Semenov, 1891), holotype (photos M. Engel 2010). 31–33 – Macrosiagon humeralis Pic, 1929. (31 – syntype; 32–33 – male from Tanzania, head frontally and metatarsomeres dorsally)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5329421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

